high_descs: Take a step to your right then walk to the stove then turn right and walk to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the knife in the mug near the bottom shelf.
Pick up the mug with the knife in it.
Turn around and walk to the white table.
Put the mug on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it on the table.

Pick up a knife on the counter.

Put the knife in the cup in the refrigerator.

Turn around and go to the table.
Put the cup on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it on the table.
